items.headline: Visit The Dork Diaries Wiki - A Site for all things Dork Diaries
items.desc: Have you ever read a book called Dork Diaries? Well this is the wiki all about that book that anyone can edit! This series of amazing books was written by Rachel Renee Russel and released on June 2, 2009. But more have been released and Dork Diaries: Tales From a Not-So Smart Miss Know-it-All or Dear Dork is under the Kiddo Awards for best children's book of 2012 and is currently winning!
